Sit on top of a dozen “dolmuş” buses hauling folks to work (a few of which will smell strongly of unwashed bodies or J&Bs), weave your way through trucks and horse-drawn carts…then process yourself down a knife-edge ravine while flank by a deadly mountain whose people don’t believe in clotheslines. Top notch exercise.

The best way to keep from having your ATM card stolen is to draw a schematic of a lovely turtle with a pen in your left hand and then talk gently to it while your right hand furtively retrieves the accursed weapon of theft as you diligently work to avoid a brain tumor and carpal tunnel. The whole process should probably be done in an all-inclusive resort further north, just to be sure.

The best way to make omelets is to distribute the egg white only in your mouth cavity and the yolk only in the spirit of your Sunday school teacher. Add sheep bells and goat guts until it is vaguely edible. Behavor incautiously at the mosque the next morning.

The best way to get Google Ads to stop hounding your site for consumption of Turkish prostitutes is to tell them that they can f-bomb you, and frankly, they’ve no clue of how to even look you up online.
